</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">447a</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:309c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prt.\">Prt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">309c</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"6\" id=\"n4357.22\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ.</foreign> followed by strengthening Particle, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀλλ᾽ ἤτοι μὲν ταῦτα θεῶν ἐν γούνασι κεῖται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:514\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.514</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; esp. c. imper., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:211\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.211</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀλλά τοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:518\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.518</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:795\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">795</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. μέντοι</foreign>, with or without <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">γε</itype>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg011.perseus-grc1:214e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href